                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 48rb: This Homily on the Saviour of the World belongs to our father Wäldä Tǝnśaʾe; and his brother (is) ʿƎquba Libanos, and his wife (is) Lahǝyä Dǝngǝl, and his children Wäldä Yoḥannǝs, Wäldä Marya[m]<m/>, Gäbrä Ḥǝywät Solomon, Wälättä Ḥǝywät, Gäbrä Giyorgis. And the scribe is Wäldä Muse. Forever and ever, Amen.</q>
                           The note mentions the donors and the scribe Wäldä Muse. It is written in the main hand.
                        </item>
